            </div>
            <div class="skill-item">
              <span class="skill-name">Vue.js</span>
              <div class="skill-bar">
                <div class="skill-progress" style="width: 70%"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Experience Highlights Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-8">Key Leadership Experiences</h2>
      <div class="experience-timeline">
        <div class="experience-item">
          <div class="experience-company">TechCorp</div>
          <div class="experience-role">Staff Software Engineer</div>
          <div class="experience-period">2021 - Present</div>
          <div class="experience-description">
            <p>Lead technical initiatives for a platform serving 50M+ users. Architect and implement scalable microservices, mentor team of 15 engineers, and drive engineering best practices.</p>
            <ul class="experience-achievements">
              <li>Designed event-driven architecture reducing system latency by 60%</li>
              <li>Led migration to Kubernetes, improving deployment frequency by 5x</li>
              <li>Established code review culture improving code quality metrics by 40%</li>
              <li>Mentored 8 engineers leading to 6 promotions within 2 years</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="experience-tech">
              <span class="tag">Node.js</span>
              <span class="tag">Go</span>
              <span class="tag">PostgreSQL</span>
              <span class="tag">Kubernetes</span>
              <span class="tag">AWS</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="experience-item">
          <div class="experience-company">StartupXYZ</div>
          <div class="experience-role">Senior Software Engineer</div>
          <div class="experience-period">2018 - 2021</div>
          <div class="experience-description">
            <p>Built core platform infrastructure from ground up for fintech startup. Designed payment processing system handling $100M+ in transactions with 99.99% availability.</p>
            <ul class="experience-achievements">
              <li>Architected payment processing system with sub-100ms response times</li>
              <li>Implemented fraud detection system reducing false positives by 80%</li>
              <li>Built CI/CD pipeline reducing deployment time from hours to minutes</li>
              <li>Established monitoring and alerting reducing incident response time by 70%</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="experience-tech">
              <span class="tag">Python</span>
              <span class="tag">PostgreSQL</span>
              <span class="tag">Redis</span>
              <span class="tag">Docker</span>
              <span class="tag">Jenkins</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="experience-item">
          <div class="experience-company">Enterprise Solutions Inc</div>
          <div class="experience-role">Software Engineer</div>
          <div class="experience-period">2016 - 2018</div>
          <div class="experience-description">
            <p>Developed enterprise web applications and learned fundamentals of scalable system design. Contributed to projects serving Fortune 500 clients.</p>
            <ul class="experience-achievements">
              <li>Built REST APIs serving 1M+ requests per day</li>
              <li>Optimized database queries improving application performance by 50%</li>
              <li>Implemented automated testing increasing code coverage to 85%</li>
              <li>Participated in on-call rotation maintaining 99.5% uptime</li>
            </ul>
